    The Armada stopped suddenly. It had reached its target: the glowing blue 
and green orb of earth. Apollo began to run through its schdualed 
preperations for scanning the area where the base was. Then, it would kill 
them all!

    Megatron found what he was looking for. The Aliens were telepathic and 
that was the key to the Armadas destruction.....or prehaps more for 
himself......
